 <span data-ttu-id="6771f-102">Transportes que usam um protocolo orientado a fluxo como TCP e pipes nomeados oferecem suporte a atualizações com base no fluxo de transporte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6771f-102">Transports that use a stream-oriented protocol such as TCP and named pipes support stream-based transport upgrades.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6771f-103">Especificamente, o Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) oferece atualizações de segurança.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6771f-103">Specifically, Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) provides security upgrades.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6771f-104">A configuração dessa segurança de transporte é encapsulada por essa classe, bem como por <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SslStreamSecurityBindingElement>, que pode ser configurado e adicionado a uma associação personalizada.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6771f-104">The configuration of this transport security is encapsulated by this class as well as by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SslStreamSecurityBindingElement>, which can be configured and added to a custom binding.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6771f-105">Além disso, um terceiro pode escrever sua próprias personalizado `StreamSecurityBindingElement`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6771f-105">In addition, a third party can write their own custom `StreamSecurityBindingElement`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6771f-106">Esses elementos de ligação de estendem o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeBindingElement> classe que é chamado para criar o fluxo de cliente e servidor de atualização de provedores.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6771f-106">These binding elements extend the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeBindingElement> class that is called to build the client and server stream upgrade providers.</span></span>  
  
