 <span data-ttu-id="6771f-114">Há três cenários em que você deve manualmente especificar o UPN/SPN correto no ponto de extremidade de cliente depois de importar o WSDL, ou especificar um personalizado <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.IdentityVerifier> sobre o cliente <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SslStreamSecurityBindingElement>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6771f-114">There are three scenarios in which you must either manually specify the correct UPN/SPN on the client endpoint after importing the WSDL, or specify a custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.IdentityVerifier> on the client’s <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.SslStreamSecurityBindingElement>.</span></span>  
  
